  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the air fryer to 375°F (190°C).",
    "Peel and chop the Korean pear into 1-inch pieces.",
    "In a small bowl, mix together the brown mustard seeds and ghee or oil.",
    "In a separate bowl, whisk together the coconut milk and shredded cheese.",
    "Heat the air fryer basket with the mustard-ghee mixture for 2 minutes.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook for 3 minutes, or until softened.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for 1 minute, or until fragrant.",
    "Add the chopped pear and cook for 2 minutes, or until tender.",
    "Pour in the coconut milk mixture and cook for 2 minutes, or until the cheese is melted and bubbly.",
    "Sprinkle with chopped cilantro and salt to taste, if using.",
    "Serve hot and enjoy!"
  ],
